📋 DESCRIPTION
Compute P_med, a scale-free probabilistic effect size
for causal mediation analysis. Provides interpretable
measures of mediation strength.

Version: 0.1.0 (first GitHub release, non-CRAN; pins medfit@v0.3.0)

